b 0\"><math alttext=\"E sub 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, what will the kinetic energy of the system be once the objects reach a common angular speed?</p>\n",
